Class Player

java.lang.Object
Code.Entity
Code.Player
Direct Known Subclasses:
Knight, Mage, Tank, Thief
public class Player extends Entity
Class has method Draw() to draw player and Attack() with player attack behaviour. Player has health points, speed of movement, attack speed and position on panel.
